{"id":246440,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/08/global-voices-智利：圣地牙哥游民/","date":"2012-08-10T20:15:07Z","modified":"2012-08-10T20:15:07Z","title":"Global Voices | 智利：圣地牙哥游民","content":"<p><p>如同世界上许多城市，在智利圣地牙哥，寒冷的冬季对游民来说是既难熬又危险。</p>\n<p>亚历杭德罗·鲁斯图姆(Alejandro Rustom)是民间记者网站Demotix的贡献者，揭露智利首都的游民现象并着重于公民团体如何给予协助。</p>\n<p>亚历杭德罗<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.demotix.com/news/1274954/chilean-homeless-make-their-way-street-santiago#.T_Wmr3CA0fE\" href=\"http://www.demotix.com/news/1274954/chilean-homeless-make-their-way-street-santiago#.T_Wmr3CA0fE\">说道</a>：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>在法兰克林区，很多住在街道上的人没有机会在像样的屋顶下生活，他们让自己成为社会边缘人。</p>\n<p>来自于特里萨大学的师生及家长组成团队，关怀这些人并提供他们粮食及衣物。内斯特查韦斯教授及校内牧歌队长认为，为了在每一次拜访都能提供适当的协助，用心聆听他们的需求是最重要的一点。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p> </p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.demotix.com/photo/1276058/pictures-homeless-chileans-get-during-night\"><img title=\"In pictures: Homeless Chileans get by during the night\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/1276058.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"560\" height=\"373\" /></a></p>\n<p>“一位女性游民坐在公园长凳上。亚历杭德罗摄，德蒙地版权所有。”</p>\n</div>\n<div><img title=\"In pictures: Homeless Chileans get by during the night\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/1275910.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"560\" height=\"373\" /></p>\n<p>“一位男性游民的笑容。亚历杭德罗摄，德蒙地版权所有。”</p>\n</div>\n<p>亚历杭德罗以摄影呈现圣地牙哥的游民如何试图生存：</p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.demotix.com/photo/1274940/chilean-homeless-make-their-way-street-santiago\"><img title=\"Chilean homeless make their way on the street - Santiago\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/1274940.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"560\" height=\"543\" /></a></p>\n<p>“玛莉亚，以卖咖啡、茶及面包为生的穷困妇人。亚历杭德罗摄，德蒙地版权所有。”</p>\n</div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.demotix.com/photo/1275943/pictures-homeless-chileans-get-during-night\"><img title=\"In pictures: Homeless Chileans get by during the night\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/1275943.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"560\" height=\"373\" /></a></p>\n<p>“以收售废纸为生的男性游民。亚历杭德罗摄，德蒙地版权所有。”</p>\n</div>\n<p>他同时也拍摄出游民如何御寒及安置休憩场地：</p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.demotix.com/photo/1275992/pictures-homeless-chileans-get-during-night\"><img title=\"In pictures: Homeless Chileans get by during the night\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/1275992.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"560\" height=\"373\" /></a></p>\n<p>“男性游民与他的狗在空地上睡觉。亚历杭德罗摄，德蒙地版权所有。”</p>\n</div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.demotix.com/photo/1275799/pictures-homeless-chileans-get-during-night\"><img title=\"In pictures: Homeless Chileans get by during the night\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/12757991.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"560\" height=\"373\" /></a></p>\n<p>“在市中心的居所，由废弃材料及捡来的家俱组成。亚历杭德罗摄，德蒙地版权所有。”</p>\n</div>\n<p>最后，亚历杭德补捉到公民团体试图改变圣地牙哥游民生活的画面：</p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.demotix.com/photo/1275824/pictures-homeless-chileans-get-during-night\"><img title=\"In pictures: Homeless Chileans get by during the night\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/1275824.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"560\" height=\"373\" /></a></p>\n<p>“一位提供食物给游民的女孩。亚历杭德罗摄，德蒙地版权所有。”</p>\n</div>\n<p>更多照片，可至亚历杭德罗－圣地牙哥游民的生活系列浏览，关于<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.demotix.com/news/1274954/chilean-homeless-make-their-way-street-santiago#.T_Wmr3CA0fE\" href=\"http://www.demotix.com/news/1274954/chilean-homeless-make-their-way-street-santiago#.T_Wmr3CA0fE\">智利游民如何在街道维持生计－圣地牙哥</a>、<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.demotix.com/news/1276199/pictures-homeless-chileans-get-during-night#.T_Wmr3CA0fE\" href=\"http://www.demotix.com/news/1276199/pictures-homeless-chileans-get-during-night#.T_Wmr3CA0fE\">照片：智利游民如何渡过夜晚</a>。</p>\n<p><small>所有照片为德蒙地版权所有。<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2010/12/15/demotix-and-global-voices-join-forces/\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2010/12/15/demotix-and-global-voices-join-forces/\">点击此</a>获得全球之声及德蒙地的合作讯息。</small></p>\n<div>校对：<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"使用者:Portnoy\" href=\"http://proj.daodin.net/mediawiki/index.php/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%80E6%99%BA%E5%88%A9%EF%BC%9A%E5%9C%A3%E5%9C%B0%E7%89%99%E5%93%A5%E6%B8%B8%E6%B0%91&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F08%2F10%2F11339%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=\"HEMiDEMi\"><span>HEMiDEMi</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://myshare.url.com.tw/index.php?func=newurl&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F08%2F10%2F11339%2F&#038;desc=%E6%99%BA%E5%88%A9%EF%BC%9A%E5%9C%A3%E5%9C%B0%E7%89%99%E5%93%A5%E6%B8%B8%E6%B0%91\" title=\"MyShare\"><span>MyShare</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.shouker.com/%22%20onclick=20js=document.createElement%20(\" title=\"Shouker\"><span>Shouker</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F08%2F10%2F11339%2F\" title=\"facebook\"><span>facebook</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F08%2F10%2F11339%2F&#038;text=%E6%99%BA%E5%88%A9%EF%BC%9A%E5%9C%A3%E5%9C%B0%E7%89%99%E5%93%A5%E6%B8%B8%E6%B0%91&#038;via=globalvoiceszh\" title=\"twitter\"><span>twitter</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://reddit.com/submit?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F08%2F10%2F11339%2F&#038;title=%E6%99%BA%E5%88%A9%EF%BC%9A%E5%9C%A3%E5%9C%B0%E7%89%99%E5%93%A5%E6%B8%B8%E6%B0%91\" title=\"reddit\"><span>reddit</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.stumbleupon.com/submit?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F08%2F10%2F11339%2F&#038;title=%E6%99%BA%E5%88%A9%EF%BC%9A%E5%9C%A3%E5%9C%B0%E7%89%99%E5%93%A5%E6%B8%B8%E6%B0%91\" title=\"StumbleUpon\"><span>StumbleUpon</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://del.icio.us/post?url=ht